OL,3,CUpdate expected on funeral directors
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FPolice are preparing to give an update
OL,7,Fon their investigation into a funeral
OL,8,Fdirectors after concerns were raised
OL,9,Fabout how it was looking after bodies.
OL,11,FThirty-five bodies were removed from
OL,12,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors
OL,13,Fon Hessle Road in Hull last month.
OL,15,FA 46-year-old man and a 23-year-old
OL,16,Fwoman have been arrested on suspicion
OL,17,Fof prevention of a lawful and decent
OL,18,Fburial, fraud by false representation
OL,19,Fand fraud by abuse of position and
OL,20,Fhave since been released on bail.
