OL,3,CUpdate expected on funeral directors
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FA report was made to Humberside police
OL,7,Fexpressing concern about the "storage
OL,8,Fand management processes relating to
OL,9,Fthe care of the deceased" at three
OL,10,Flocations run by Legacy Independent
OL,11,FFuneral Directors on Wednesday, 6
OL,12,FMarch.
OL,14,FPolice said that several enquiries
OL,15,Fwere made afterwards to "ascertain the
OL,16,Fexact details, concern and
OL,17,Fcircumstances".
