OL,3,CUpdate expected on funeral directors
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FThe next day, Humberside Police
OL,7,Fconfirmed it was in the process of
OL,8,Fmoving "a number of deceased" from the
OL,9,Fpremises on Hessle Road to the
OL,10,Fcouncil's mortuary.
OL,12,FThe force said a "quantity" of
OL,13,Fsuspected human ashes had also been
OL,14,Frecovered and were being
OL,15,F"respectfully" moved.
OL,17,FOn Friday, 15 March, the force said it
OL,18,Fhad contacted the families of the 35
OL,19,Fpeople whose bodies had been moved.
